      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Dawn of the Kestodon",
        "Client": "Utterly Confused Man",
        "Description": "What do I do? WHAT DO I DO!?\r\nThere\u0027s Kestodon all around me!\r\nHere, there, yonder, whither\u2014\r\nthey\u0027re everywhere, I tell ya,\r\nEVERYWHERE! Even in my mind!\r\nThere\u0027s nowhere left to run! You\r\ngotta stop \u0027em before it\u0027s too late!",
        "Target": "Slay 20 Kestodon",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "L\u0027invasion des Kestodon",
        "Client": "Un homme d\u00E9sesp\u00E9r\u00E9",
        "Description": "J\u0027en peux plus ! Les Kestodon sont\r\npartout ! PARTOUT ! Ils m\u0027observent\r\ntout le temps, m\u00EAme dans mes r\u00EAves !\r\nIl faut que tu les \u00E9limines avant\r\nqu\u0027ils prennent le pouvoir !\r\nJe t\u0027en prie !",
        "Target": "Tuer 20 Kestodon",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "L\u0027alba del Kestodon",
        "Client": "Uomo molto confuso",
        "Description": "Cosa faccio? COSA FACCIO?!\r\nI Kestodon non mi danno\r\ntregua! Qua, l\u00E0, su, gi\u00F9...\r\nSono dappertutto, DAPPERTUTTO!\r\nPersino nella mia testa! Non\r\nc\u0027\u00E8 via di scampo! Fermali\r\nprima che sia troppo tardi!",
        "Target": "Uccidi 20 Kestodon",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "D\u00E4mmerung der Kestodon",
        "Client": "V\u00F6llig verwirrter Mann",
        "Description": "Was mach ich blo\u00DF? WAS MACH\r\nICH BLOSS?! Um mich rum sind\r\nKestodon! Links, rechts, hier,\r\ndort \u2013 sie sind \u00DCBERALL! Sogar in\r\nmeinem Kopf! Ich kann nirgend-\r\nwohin! Halt sie auf, bevor es zu\r\nsp\u00E4t ist!",
        "Target": "Erlege 20 Kestodon.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "\u00A1Kestodon a patadas!",
        "Client": "Tipo muy confundido",
        "Description": "\u00A1Ay, \u00BFqu\u00E9 hago?! \u00A1Kestodon!\r\n\u00A1En los Llanos arenosos! Aqu\u00ED,\r\nall\u00ED... \u00A1Mires donde mires!\r\nTe digo que est\u00E1n por todas\r\npartes, \u00A1incluso en mi cabeza!\r\n\u00A1No hay escapatoria! Por\r\nfavor, \u00A1acaba con ellos!",
        "Target": "Abate 20 Kestodon",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
